Krak Missiles are anti-armor warheads, designed for piercing through thick armor plating and bringing down heavily fortified targets. These missiles carry a concentrated charge that delivers a devastating punch upon impact, making them the weapon of choice when facing vehicles, bunkers, or monstrous creatures. The high-explosive power of a Krak Missile focuses its destructive force into a single, armor-shattering impact, capable of tearing through even the most resilient defenses. Space Marines rely on Krak Missiles to neutralize enemy armor and hardpoints, ensuring that nothing stands in the way of their advance.

**Lightning Claw**		

