The Power Axe is a devastating melee weapon favored by those Space Marines who prize raw destructive force over speed. Wreathed in a crackling energy field that disrupts molecular bonds upon contact, the Power Axe channels its disruptive energy along a broad, single-edged blade designed for cleaving through the heaviest armor. The weapon's top-heavy design delivers blows of tremendous force, capable of splitting Terminator plate and vehicle hulls alike, though the weight and momentum of each swing demands a measured, deliberate fighting style.

Among the Adeptus Astartes, Power Axes are often carried by veterans and sergeants who have earned the right to wield such potent weapons. Some Chapters favor the Power Axe for its symbolic value as well—the Blood Angels associate it with the executioner's duty, while the Space Wolves see it as an echo of their Fenrisian heritage. Regardless of tradition, a Space Marine armed with a Power Axe becomes a breacher of the highest order, capable of shattering defensive lines and felling even the most heavily armored foes with each devastating stroke.

**Power Fist**			

