The Power Fist is an iconic symbol of brute strength and overwhelming force, wielded by the mightiest warriors of the Imperium. This massive gauntlet, encased in a shimmering energy field, multiplies the user's strength to unimaginable levels, allowing them to crush through armor, flesh, and even the thickest ceramite with ease. Each strike from a Power Fist lands with the force of a thunderous hammer, pulverizing anything it touches into ruin. Though cumbersome and slow compared to other weapons, the sheer destructive power of a Power Fist makes it a fearsome tool in close combat, often turning the tide of battle in a single, devastating blow.

**Power Maul**		

