The Thunder Hammer is one of the most destructive melee weapons available to the Adeptus Astartes, a massive weapon whose head is fitted with an energy field generator that releases a devastating shockwave upon impact. Each blow from a Thunder Hammer strikes with the force of a cannon shell, the energy discharge detonating with a thunderous crack that can shatter Terminator plate, crush vehicle hulls, and reduce even the largest xenos monstrosities to broken ruin. The weapon doubles the wielder's already formidable strength, ensuring that nothing short of a titan's armor can withstand a direct hit.  
Despite its awesome power, the Thunder Hammer is a demanding weapon to wield. Its sheer mass and the charging cycle of its energy field generator make it slower than other melee weapons, requiring its bearer to commit fully to each swing. This makes the Thunder Hammer the domain of only the strongest and most experienced warriors—Terminators, Captains, and champions who can absorb punishment while waiting for the perfect moment to deliver a single, war-ending blow. Paired with a Storm Shield, a Thunder Hammer-armed Space Marine becomes an almost unstoppable force, a walking embodiment of the Emperor's judgment made manifest in ceramite and crackling energy.

