The Volkite Culverin is an ancient and revered weapon, dating back to the earliest days of the Imperium. Designed to fire streams of searing energy, this potent relic vaporizes flesh and bone with terrifying efficiency. Each burst from a Volkite Culverin unleashes a wave of destructive thermic energy, capable of incinerating multiple foes in a single, devastating salvo. Though its complex and esoteric technology has largely been lost to time, the Volkite Culverin remains a prized possession among the Astartes, its fearsome firepower a testament to the forgotten mastery of mankind's distant past.

